        "description": "以生物正十六烷为模型化合物，在Pt/SAPO-11催化剂上评价其加氢异构化性能。考察了温度、空速、氢烃比、压力和金属负载量对正十六烷转化率和异十六烷选择性的影响。",
        "text_snippet": "The hydroisomerization performance of the catalyst was evaluated with bio-n-hexadecane as the model compound... Under the conditions of 340◦C, 1.5 MPa, WHSV=1.0 h−1, V(H2):V(n-hexadecane)=1000:1, the conversion of n-hexadecane and the selectivity of i-hexadecane were 81.8% and 86.5%, respectively.",
